            "id": "devotion",
            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20verse%20God%20shows%20His%20desire%20to%20reveal%20His%20plans%20to%20His%20servants%20before%20events%20take%20place.%20God%20does%20not%20just%20spring%20events%20on%20nations.%20He%20gradually%20warns%20them%20of%20coming%20disaster%2C%20as%20He%20did%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Jonah%20and%20Nineveh.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20book%20of%20Revelation%20was%20written%20to%20seven%20different%20%22angels%22%20of%20the%20seven%20churches%20of%20Asia.%20Most%20commentators%20believe%20that%20these%20angels%20were%20the%20pastors%20of%20those%20churches.%20The%20local%20pastors%20received%20revelation%20from%20the%20Holy%20Spirit%20of%20God's%20intention%20toward%20their%20churches.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIn%20our%20churches%20today%2C%20if%20the%20pastor%20needs%20to%20repent%2C%20the%20Holy%20Spirit%20will%20convict%20the%20leader%20or%20use%20circumstances%20to%20force%20him%20to%20face%20an%20issue.%20This%20leading%20by%20the%20Holy%20Spirit%20protects%20the%20flock%2C%20since%20the%20local%20church%20will%20follow%20the%20leader%20in%20either%20the%20right%20or%20wrong%20direction.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIf%20you%20are%20concerned%20about%20the%20direction%20of%20your%20church%2C%20pray%20for%20your%20pastor.%20God%20has%20obligated%20Himself%20to%20speak%20to%20him%2C%20so%20pray%2C%20asking%20the%20Lord%20to%20give%20your%20pastor%20the%20courage%20to%20obey%20as%20he%20hears%20God%20speaking.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
